\"zDocsAiSummaryContaineruniface_104dww1665702582302.html\"></div><div><article class=\"hascomments\" data-page=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dww1665702582302.html\" id=\"bundle:uniface_104/enus/dww1665702582302.html\"><main role=\"main\"><article aria-labelledby=\"ariaid-title1\" class=\"dita\" id=\"dww1665702582302\" role=\"article\">\n<h1 class=\"title topictitle1\" id=\"ariaid-title1\">\n      Service\n </h1>\n<div class=\"body refbody\"><p class=\"shortdesc\">A Service is a Component that defines a business logic component, which provides processing that does not require user interaction.\n </p>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dww1665702582302__section_yby_kzn_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1238537e51\">Characteristics</h2>\n<div class=\"table-wrap\"><table class=\"table\" count-columns=\"2\" id=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1\"><caption></caption><colgroup><col/><col/></colgroup><thead class=\"thead\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Characteristics</p>\n</th>\n<th class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" id=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__2\"></th>\n</tr>\n</thead><tbody class=\"tbody\">\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Icon:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\"><img alt=\"Icon\" class=\"image\" id=\"dww1665702582302__image_xxc_nzn_mwb\" src=\"https://docs-be.rocketsoftware.com/bundle/uniface_104/page/component.png?_LANG=enus\"/></p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Object type code:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<span class=\"keyword cmdname\">cpt</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Main Development Object?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">Yes</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Has layout?</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">No</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Part of:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Contains:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"yth1665702550544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/yth1665702550544.html\" title=\"A Component Entity is a Development Object that represents data that is owned by a Component. It is part of the Component’s structure and is maintained as part of the Component, although it may reference and inherit from a Modeled Entity.\">Component Entity</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyt1665702609153.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyt1665702609153.html\" title=\"A Label is a Development Object that contains text that appears on a presentation component. Labels have properties, but most cannot be set dynamically.\">Label</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jgi1665702550212.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jgi1665702550212.html\" title=\"A Property is a named, typed attribute of Development Object that defines a characteristic or behavior of the object. Each property has a descriptive name, a literal name, a data type, and a value. If no value is specified, a default value may be used.\">Property</a>, <a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cny1665702550298.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cny1665702550298.html\" title=\"A Code Container is a type of Property that holds code, such as ProcScript, JavaScript, or HTML. It can contain one or more code modules, such as triggers, operations, functions, or entries, or HTML for the layout.\">Code Container</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Generalization:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ifc1665702608950.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ifc1665702608950.html\" title=\"A Component is a Main Development Object that defines an executable part of an application. It defines the data structure used to access data, the layout (if applicable) used to present it, and the actions used to modify, validate, and store data.\">Component</a>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Specializations:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">—</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">Compilation output:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ird1665702714456.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ird1665702714456.html\" title=\"A Signature is a Development Object that describes the remote interface of a component, or modeled entity operation. Signatures for Uniface components and modeled entity operations are automatically generated, but signatures for non-Uniface components that Uniface can call at runtime, must be explicitly defined.\">Signature</a>, <span class=\"ph filepath\">\n<var class=\"keyword varname\">ServiceName</var>.svc</span>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n<tr class=\"row\" dir=\"ltr\">\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__1\">\n<p class=\"p\">URI format:</p>\n</td>\n<td class=\"entry\" dir=\"ltr\" headers=\"dww1665702582302__table_d10604e1_d10605e1_d10606e1__entry__2\">\n<p class=\"p\">\n<code class=\"ph codeph\">cpt:<var class=\"keyword varname\">ServiceName</var>\n</code>\n</p>\n</td>\n</tr>\n</tbody></table></div>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dww1665702582302__section_bsr_4zn_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1238537e305\">Specialization</h2>\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dww1665702582302__p_d95600e1_d95601e1_d95602e1\">Service specializes Component in the following ways:</p>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dww1665702582302__ul_wp3_pzn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38345e1_d38346e1_d38347e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dww1665702582302__p_d95603e1_d95604e1_d95605e1\">It has no layout.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38348e1_d38349e1_d38350e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dww1665702582302__p_d95606e1_d95607e1_d95608e1\">It has no user interface triggers.</p>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38351e1_d38352e1_d38353e1\">\n<p class=\"p\" id=\"dww1665702582302__p_d95609e1_d95610e1_d95611e1\">It compiles to a runtime object and a signature.</p>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dww1665702582302__section_ujq_pzn_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1238537e335\">Properties</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dww1665702582302__ul_us5_rzn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d37985e1_d37986e1_d37987e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"jrq1665702585385.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/jrq1665702585385.html\" title=\"Name of the development object, which uniquely identifies it.\">Name</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d37988e1_d37989e1_d37990e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"owq1665702585461.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/owq1665702585461.html\" title=\"Type of Development Object. Read only.\">Type</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d37991e1_d37992e1_d37993e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ybn1665702585544.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ybn1665702585544.html\" title=\"Complete URI of the Development Object. Read only.\">Location</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d37994e1_d37995e1_d37996e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xrw1665702585620.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xrw1665702585620.html\" title=\"Use this property to briefly describe the development object in up to 256 Unicode characters.\">Description</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d37997e1_d37998e1_d37999e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ipc1665702585697.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ipc1665702585697.html\" title=\"Use this property to provide comments or instructions for the selected development object. You can use the toolbar and standard Windows keyboard shortcuts to format the text, copy and paste, and undo and redo edits.\">Documentation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dww1665702582302__ul_et5_rzn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38000e1_d38001e1_d38002e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"cnn1665702762358.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/cnn1665702762358.html\" title=\"Read-only property the records the date and time when the object was last modified. The value is set by Uniface.\">Date Modified</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dww1665702582302__ul_gt5_rzn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38003e1_d38004e1_d38005e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"wyl1665702688770.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/wyl1665702688770.html\" title=\"Specifies the library containing the global objects used by the component or application shell. If no library is specified, the library defined for the application shell is used. Otherwise, SYSTEM_LIBRARY is used as the default.\">Library</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38006e1_d38007e1_d38008e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dfn1665702688838.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dfn1665702688838.html\" title=\"This property determines whether the component is a modeled component.\">Is Modeled Component</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38009e1_d38010e1_d38011e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mwa1665702688914.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mwa1665702688914.html\" title=\"This property specifies the name of the modeled component from which this component is derived.\">Modeled Component</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dww1665702582302__ul_mt5_rzn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38012e1_d38013e1_d38014e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"obc1665703043525.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/obc1665703043525.html\" title=\"Specifies the type of Uniface Component.\">Component Type</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38015e1_d38016e1_d38017e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qsg1665702688984.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qsg1665702688984.html\" title=\"Determines the degree to which data in the component can be edited and stored.\">Data Access</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38018e1_d38019e1_d38020e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ypq1665702689055.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ypq1665702689055.html\" title=\"Specifies whether the component definition is cached in memory.\">Component Behavior</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38021e1_d38022e1_d38023e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"xhw1665702689197.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/xhw1665702689197.html\" title=\"Determines whether the component can run on a server without reference to global objects or a user interface. Valid values are T or F (default).\">Self-Contained</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38024e1_d38025e1_d38026e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mxz1665703028639.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mxz1665703028639.html\" title=\"Controls whether the component instance runs in attached mode, meaning that it is created by another component and is deleted when the parent component instance is deleted.\">Attachment</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dww1665702582302__ul_vt5_rzn_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38027e1_d38028e1_d38029e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"iku1665702689266.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/iku1665702689266.html\" title=\"Name of the Keyboard Translation Table used to interpret field data upon input.\">Input Translation</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38030e1_d38031e1_d38032e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"dbe1665702689335.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/dbe1665702689335.html\" title=\"Name of the Keyboard Translation Table used to convert field data upon output.\">Output Translation</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n<section class=\"section\" id=\"dww1665702582302__section_udm_114_mwb\"><h2 class=\"title sectiontitle\" id=\"d1238537e522\">Triggers and Operations</h2>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dww1665702582302__ul_x1l_b14_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38402e1_d38403e1_d38404e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"kez1665702582531.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/kez1665702582531.html\" title=\"Handles processing when an Accept request is received, usually with the intention of closing the component and keeping all changes made on it. This trigger is exposed as an operation in the component signature.\">trigger accept</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38405e1_d38406e1_d38407e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"hmn1665702683413.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/hmn1665702683413.html\" title=\"System trigger that provides component-specific post-processing.\">trigger postActivate</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38408e1_d38409e1_d38410e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"muo1665702683268.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/muo1665702683268.html\" title=\"System trigger that provides component-specific pre-processing. It is required in web applications to recreate the component state.\">trigger preActivate</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38411e1_d38412e1_d38413e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"ghq1665702608876.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/ghq1665702608876.html\" title=\"Reacts to asynchronous messages that come from outside the application.\">trigger receiveMessage</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38414e1_d38415e1_d38416e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"qun1665702582075.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/qun1665702582075.html\" title=\"Trigger that handles processing when a Quit request is received, usually with the intention of closing the component without saving any modifications made in it. This trigger is exposed as an operation in the component signature.\">trigger quit</a>\n</li>\n</ul>\n<ul class=\"ul\" id=\"dww1665702582302__ul_jbl_b14_mwb\">\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38417e1_d38418e1_d38419e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"mkf1719505969039.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/mkf1719505969039.html\" title=\"Default component operation, which is invoked by the activate statement.\">operation exec</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38420e1_d38421e1_d38422e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"zye1719506814289.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/zye1719506814289.html\" title=\"Defines the component behavior when a component instance is created with newinstance (or by activate when newinstance is executed implicitly).\">operation init</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38423e1_d38424e1_d38425e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tcd1719504517290.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tcd1719504517290.html\" title=\"Defines the component behavior when a component instance is removed.\">operation cleanup</a>\n</li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38426e1_d38427e1_d38428e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"tdr1719503726176.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/tdr1719503726176.html\" title=\"Defines the behavior that should occur in response to an Accept request. If an Accept trigger is defined, it is exposed as the accept operation in the component signature.\">operation accept</a></li>\n<li class=\"li\" id=\"dww1665702582302__li_d38429e1_d38430e1_d38431e1\">\n<a class=\"xref\" data-bundleid=\"uniface_104\" data-navpath=\"icw1719507043571.html\" href=\"/de-DE/bundle/uniface_104/page/icw1719507043571.html\" title=\"Defines the processing that should occur during a Quit request. If a quit trigger is defined in a component, it is exposed as the quit operation in the component signature.\">operation quit</a></li>\n</ul>\n</section>\n</div>\n</article></main></article>\n</div></div></div><div class=\"bottomFeedback\"><div aria-labelledby=\"bottomFeedbackText\" class=\"bottomFeedbackContent\" role=\"group\"><span class=\"bottomFeedbackText\" id=\"bottomFeedbackText\">Was this topic helpful?</span><div class=\"bottomFeedbackButtonGroup\"><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612690\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-up\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-up\"></use></svg><span>Like</span></a><a data-backdrop=\"static\" data-target=\"#feedbackModal_bottom_3612690\" data-toggle=\"modal\" href=\"#\" role=\"button\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-thumbs-down\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-thumbs-down\"></use></svg><span>Dislike</span></a></div></div></div><div style=\"position: fixed; bottom: 170px; right: 70px; cursor: pointer; transition-duration: 0.2s; transition-timing-function: linear; transition-delay: 0s; z-index: 3; opacity: 0; visibility: hidden; transition-property: opacity, visibility;\"><button aria-label=\"Scroll to top\" class=\"zDocsScrollTopBtn\" data-tooltip-content=\"Scroll to top\" data-tooltip-id=\"zDocsBackToTopToolTip\" id=\"zDocsScrollToTop\" type=\"button\"><svg aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"ico-next\"><use xlink:href=\"#ico-next\"></use></svg></button></div></body></html>", "text": "Service Add to My Topics Add selected topic and subtopics Add Topic & Subtopics with topic head Add entire publication Watch Download PDF Save selected topic Save selected topic and subtopics Save entire publication Share Email Link Copy Link Feedback Last Updated Okt 09, 2024 Summarize Uniface 10.4 Service A Service is a Component that defines a business logic component, which provides processing that does not require user interaction. Characteristics Characteristics Icon: Object type code: cpt Main Development Object? Yes Has layout? No Part of: — Contains: Component Entity , Label , Property , Code Container Generalization: Component Specializations: — Compilation output: Signature , ServiceName .svc URI format: cpt: ServiceName Specialization Service specializes Component in the following ways: It has no layout. It has no user interface triggers. It compiles to a runtime object and a signature. Properties Name Type Location Description Documentation Date Modified Library Is Modeled Component Modeled Component Component Type Data Access Component Behavior Self-Contained Attachment Input Translation Output Translation Triggers and Operations trigger accept trigger postActivate trigger preActivate trigger receiveMessage trigger quit operation exec operation init operation cleanup operation accept operation quit Was this topic helpful? Like Dislike"}